'''Havridam City''' was one of the largest [[City/Legends|cities]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[New Bakstre]]. The [[Mechanical Liberation Front]] partially destroyed the city in an attempt to free a shipment of [[Vindicator XM-15 "brilliant" missile|Vindicator XM-15 missiles]]. When the attack ensued, the missiles detonated, killing 14 MLF members and destroying a 25-[[Kilometer/Legends|kilometer]] radius of the city.

